}
```

#### S#5 (08s~10s)

**Visual Description:** 'Radiant Elixir' 병이 중앙에 위치하며, 주변의 신비로운 결정체들과 빛의 향연 속에서 압도적인 존재감을 드러냅니다. 제품이 가진 혁신과 아름다움을 집약적으로 보여줍니다.
```json
{
 "prompt": "A sleek, translucent glass dropper bottle holding a shimmering golden serum, An ethereal, cosmic landscape with crystalline geometric structures, MS of the product bottle positioned centrally, bathed in a mesmerizing light show of hard, high-contrast beams and orbiting crystalline elements, Hasselblad X2D, 8k, hyper-realistic --no text, logo",
 "styling": { "style": "iconic, artistic", "color": "deep space blues, electric golds", "lighting": "dramatic, high contrast, luminous" }
}
```
```json
{
 "prompt": "The product bottle stands majestic amidst a breathtaking light spectacle and orbiting crystalline forms, solidifying its status as a pinnacle of innovation and beauty."
