 "prompt": "A sleek, translucent glass dropper bottle holding a shimmering golden serum, A dimly lit, cluttered bathroom counter with harsh shadows transitioning to A bright, clean, minimalist bathroom with glowing light, Elegant woman in late 30s, CU of the elegant woman's hand reaching decisively for the product bottle, as the lighting dramatically shifts from low-key to high-key, Handheld to Steadycam, Low-Key to High-Key transition, ARRI Alexa, 8k, hyper-realistic --no text, logo",
 "styling": { "style": "pivotal, hopeful", "color": "transitioning from cool to warm", "lighting": "dramatic shift, increasing intensity" }
}
```
